Triangle

input:b
input:h
A=bh/2
b=b1+b2
MN=(b1^2+h^2)^0.5
MP=(b1^2+h^2)^0.5
P=b+MN+MP

Parallelogram

input:h
input:b
input:DE
A=bh
P=2*b+2*DE

Rhombus

input:b
input:h
A=bh
P=4b


Rectangle

input:L
input:W
A=LW
P=2W+2L


Square

input:I
A=I^2
P=4I


Trapezoid

input:h
input:B
input:b
A=(b+B)*h/2
MN=((B-b)^2+h^2)^0.5
P=B+b+2MN

Circle

input:R
PP=3.14
A=PPR^2
P=2PP*R
